  "general_provisions": "This bill addresses eggs.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>defines and modifies terms;<hr><ltbullet>clarifies fee and rulemaking authority for the Department of Agriculture and Food (department) regarding the distribution, sale, and inspection of shell eggs;<hr><ltbullet>establishes that a person may not:<hr><ltbullet1>distribute shell eggs unless the person obtains a license from the department; or<hr><ltbullet1>sell shell eggs from a small producer outside of the state;<hr><ltbullet>requires a large egg producer to register with the department as a food establishment;<hr><ltbullet>clarifies the requirements for small and large egg producers; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical and conforming changes.",
